<p>Emergency Shelter Hotline: 617-573-1106</p>
<p><span style="font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif">Find emergency shelter locations <a href="https://www.mass.gov/how-to/find-emergency-family-shelter" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here.</a></span></p>
